OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FCovid: US halves isolation 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Ftime for asymptomatic      
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Finfection                  
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, US health officials have halved the    
OL,6, recommended isolation time for people  
OL,7, with asymptomatic Covid-19 from 10 to  
OL,8, five days, amid a surge in cases.      
OL,10,FThe measure is expected to alleviate   
OL,11,Fdisruption caused by staff shortages in
OL,12,Fmany areas because of infections.      
OL,14,FThe Centers for Disease Control (CDC)  
OL,15,Fsays most transmissions happen in the  
OL,16,Ftwo days before and three days after   
OL,17,Fsymptoms develop.                      
OL,19,FBut experts have criticised the lack of
OL,20,Ftesting requirements to end isolation. 
